14.3**16
# Remember that ** can be read as 'to the power of',即相当于3^16次方. 3**16 is about 43 million.

15.Python中的大于小于等于的比较和true，false的判断与Java相同
not is evaluated first;
and is evaluated next;
or is evaluated last.


